swagger.content:
swagger: '2.0'
info:
  description: API use to get some values
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger demo API
  termsOfService: 'https://www.maif.fr/terms/'
  contact:
    email: demo@daikoku.io
host: 'api.oto.tools'
basePath: /
schemes:
  - http
paths:
  /contrats:
    get:
      tags:
        - values
      summary: some demo values
      description: Return demo values
      operationId: findAll
      produces:
        - application/json
      responses:
        '200':
          description: success
          schema:
            $ref: '#/definitions/Values'
        '204':
          description: No values found
      security:
        - api_key: []
securityDefinitions:
  api_key:
    type: apiKey
    name: key
    in: query
definitions:
  Values:
    type: object
    required:
      - label
      - caller
      - env
      - values
    properties:
      label:
        type: string
        description: 'The data label, contextualized in relation to the caller and the environment'
        example: raw values for caller
      env:
        type: string
        description: The environment
        example: prod
      caller:
        type: string
        description: Caller ID
        example: caller
      values:
        type: array
        description: Values
        example:
          - 123
          - 124
          - 125
        items:
          type: number

payload.content:
# How to use api

to use demo api, get an apikey and run the following command in a terminal

```sh
curl -X GET http://api.oto.tools -u <your credentials> | jq
```
